certain EGP categories.{title:References}{p 0 4}Erikson, R., J.H. Goldthorpe, L. Portocarero. 1979.{it:International class mobility in three Westen European Countries:England, France, and Sweden.}British Journal of Sociology 30: 415-451.{p 0 4}Ganzeboom, H.B.G., de Graaf, P.M. & D.J. Treiman. 1992.{it:A Standard International Socio-Economic Index of Occupational Status.}Social Science Research 21: 1-56.{p 0 4}ILO (International Labour Office). 1968.{it:International Standard Classification of Occupations, revised edition.}Geneva: International Labour Office.Direct comments to:{p 4 4}{browse "mailto:John_Hendrickx@yahoo.com": John Hendrickx}{break}Management Studies Group{break}Wageningen University{break}Hollandseweg 1{break}6706 KN Wageningen{break}The Netherlands{break}{p}The {cmd:isco} package is available at{browse "http://ideas.uqam.ca/ideas/data/bocbocode.html":SSC-IDEAS}.Use {help ssc} {cmd:install isco} to obtain the latest version.{title:Also see}{p 0 21}On-line: help for  {help isco}, {help iscoisei}, {help iscotrei}, {help isco6888}, {help iscolab},  {help isko}, {help iskoegp}, {help iskoisei}, {help iskotrei}, {help isko8868}, {help iskolab}{p_end}